DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe have the pleasure of inviting y
 ou to our ConvergenceTalk series for spring 2026 which will be every secon
 d Friday. We will update the individual invitations with speaker and title
  as they are planned. Invitations conflicting with other planned activitie
 s will of course be deleted.\n\nThe talks are held at PharmaDataHub@UCPH\,
  Jagtvej 160\, 1st floor\, and it is also possible to participate via Team
 s. You are very welcome to join our ConvergenceCoffee from 8:30-9:00.\n\nL
 ooking forward to seeing you to our exiting talks.\n\nBest\,\nMarin Matic
 & Jeppe Hartmann\n________________________________________________________
