SEQUENCE:76
DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe invite you to a very exciting a
 nd inspiring ConvergenceTalk by Casper Steinmann\, Flipped Classrooms and
 Mild Academic Chaos.\n\nCasper is Associate Professor at the Department of
  Physics\, Chemistry and Pharmacy\, SDU. Casper is also associated with CP
 DSE as group leader.\n\nThe talk is held at PharmaDataHub@UCPH\, Jagtvej 1
 60\, 1st floor\, and it is also possible to participate via Teams. You are
  very welcome to join our ConvergenceCoffee from 8:30-9:00.\n\nLooking for
 ward to seeing you.\n\nBest\,\nMarin Matic & Jeppe Hartmann\n_____________
