SEQUENCE:10
DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe are looking forward to seeing y
 ou to our episode meeting.\n\nLocation\nWe will have this meeting at UCPH\
 , Department of Science Education (IND) – thank you\, Morten for hosting
 .\n\nWe will be in room 0H154. Enter from Rådmandsgade 64\, the room is o
 n the ground floor.\n\nAgenda – we also would like your contribution\nYo
 u can find the agenda for the meeting attached and [​docx icon]  here<ht
 tps://alumni.sharepoint.com/:w:/r/sites/UCPH_CPDSE377/Shared%20Documents/O
 rganization%20and%20Community/Episode%20meetings/Episode%20Meeting%20May%2
 019%202026%20at%20KU/Agenda%20CPDSE%20Episode%20Meeting%20260519.docx?d=w2
 01e285161fb4c0083268e5918537a21&csf=1&web=1&e=NTvR9u>. Based on the feedba
 ck from the last meeting we have extended the meeting with half an hour to
  have more time to network and talk.\n\nAs a part of the check-in\, we wou
 ld also very much like for you to share any announcements or anything you
 celebrate. That could be related to research\, big stuff\, birthdays\, new
  hires etc.\n\nLanyard and name tag\nWe kindly ask that you bring your CPD
 SE lanyard and name tag (if you got one at the last episode meeting).\n\nL
 unch\nWe will be serving lunch at the meeting\, so we kindly ask that you
 reply to the invitation\, so we know how many people to expect. If you hav
 e any dietary restrictions/allergies\, please let Jeppe (jeppe.hartmann@su
 nd.ku.dk<mailto:jeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk>) know no later than 11 May 2026
 .\n\nTransportation\nIf you are going by car to the meeting\, we hope that
  you will be able to give others a lift. We kindly ask that you register o
 n this [​xlsx icon]  Excel sheet<https://alumni.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/sit
 es/UCPH_CPDSE377/Shared%20Documents/Organization%20and%20Community/Episode
 %20meetings/Episode%20Meeting%20May%2019%202026%20at%20KU/CPDSE%20episode%
 20meeting%20May%2019\,%202026%20-%20transportation.xlsx?d=w35136004d504435
 fb38a3217800cbd94&csf=1&web=1&e=0QS40V> if you have room in your car and f
 or those of you who would like to get a lift to register in the same sheet
 .\n\nLooking forward to seeing you.\n\nBest\,\nLykke\, Lucy\, & Jeppe\n\nJ
 eppe Hartmann\nProject Coordinator\n\nUniversity of Copenhagen\nDepartment
  of Drug Design and Pharmacology\n\nUniversitetsparken 2\nDK - 2100 Copenh
 agen\nDenmark\nLync/Skype +45 35323413\njeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk<mailto:j
 eppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk>\n\n[Logo for Københavns Universitet]\n\nHow we
 protect personal data<https://informationssikkerhed.ku.dk/english/protecti
 on-of-information-privacy/privacy-policy/>\n\n\n
SUMMARY;LANGUAGE=en-US:CPDSE Episode Meeting
LOCATION;LANGUAGE=en-US:UCPH\, Department of Science Education\, room 0H154
 . Enter from Rådmandsgade 64\, the room is on the ground floor
