DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe have the pleasure of inviting y
 ou to our CPDSE center retreat. We have chosen the date where most of you
 have indicated that you were able to attend.\n\nThe retreat will be both t
 he season finale for season 3 and kickoff of season 4. As always\, we will
  of course have time to network\, to talk\, to play games etc.\n\nWe will
 send you the agenda for the retreat as well as information about the venue
 .\n\nPlease reach out to Jeppe (jeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk<mailto:jeppe.har
 tmann@sund.ku.dk>) if you have any questions.\n\nAll the best from the pla
 nning group\nJacob\, Lucy\, Lykke\, Stefan & Jeppe\n\nJeppe Hartmann\nProj
 ect Coordinator\n\nUniversity of Copenhagen\nDepartment of Drug Design and
  Pharmacology\n\nUniversitetsparken 2\nDK - 2100 Copenhagen\nDenmark\nPhon
 e +45 35323413\njeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk<mailto:jeppe.hartmann@sund.ku.dk
 >\n\n[Logo for Københavns Universitet]\n\nHow we protect personal data<ht
 tps://informationssikkerhed.ku.dk/english/protection-of-information-privac
 y/privacy-policy/>\n\n\n
