DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Dear all\,\n\nWe have the pleasure of inviting y
 ou to CPDSE Connect meetings in 2026.\n\nThese meetings are a short check-
 in between our episode meetings to update you on what is going on in CPDSE
 . The meetings will only be online.\n\nAgenda for the meetings:\n\n11:00-1
 1:15: Announcements\n\n  *   News from the circles\n  *   Basecamp highlig
 hts\n  *   AI Tips & Tricks\n\n11:15-11:30: Feature: “Implementing UClou
 d in an elective data-science course for pharmacy students: Some experienc
 es and reflections” by Anders Østergaard Madsen (IF)\n\nLooking forward
  to connecting with you.\n\nBest regards\,\nJacob Fredegaard Hansen & Jepp
 e Hartmann\n______________________________________________________________
